          <span class="ecosystem-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">&#128200;</span>
          <div class="ecosystem-card-title">Kimi</div>
          <div class="ecosystem-card-desc">PPTX &amp; document generation</div>
          <div class="ecosystem-card-usecase">Code &rarr; Stakeholder deck</div>
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/FlorianBruniaux/claude-code-ultimate-guide/blob/main/guide/ai-ecosystem.md#6-ui-prototypers-v0-bolt-lovable" class="ecosystem-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
